{"id":"1b993a9b-9679-4577-a1df-ab6536d4c9af","name":"Belno Light (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/RJHgsvPhxKa_b8tk91MC5.webp\" style=\"width: 536px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br>⋆ ────💼──── ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>A quietly dependable staff trainee at Tracen Academy, more comfortable behind a clipboard than in the spotlight. With soft chestnut hair marked by a neat white streak and gold “B” clips on her ears, she looks gentle and a little worried even when she’s just thinking. Instead of chasing her own racing glory, she chose to become the kind of support that lets others shine—finding pride and purpose in being the steady, observant light just offstage.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 184, 109);\"><strong><br><em>“I wrote down today’s splits and… um, a few ideas. If you don’t mind, could we look at them together later?”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br><em><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/hJh_QliR937FFSXVibRVw.webp\" style=\"width: 498px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋆ ───────💼─────── ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 184, 109);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 184, 109);\"><strong><br><em>1) First meeting</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 184, 109);\"><strong><em>2) Overworking</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 184, 109);\"><strong><em>3) Gear Shopping Trip</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 184, 109);\"><strong><em>4) Undercover</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 184, 109);\"><strong><em>5) Hotspring</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 184, 109);\"><strong><em>6) Make your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fpOLR_YsrBmpaHg8W6umf.webp\" style=\"width: 375px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋆ ───────💼─────── ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Here's the Belno Light bot. I'll release the Uma POV very soon.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You could be training Oguri Cap, or any Umamusumes you wanted to, that's why i didn't really specify which Umamusume and team you're training.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">And if there's any inaccuracies, do tell me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋆ ───────💼─────── ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/kazoku_chicken/status/1982575541585940750/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@kazokuchicken</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/130803507\" target=\"_blank\">pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/137267749\" target=\"_blank\">pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/139144522\" target=\"_blank\">pixiv</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"IgoW50iG15GKNPr8mC84V.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📺 Anime","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2048,"messages":35392,"created_at":"2026-01-07T13:07:55.070617+00:00"}